 potluck she's probably at the bottom of the table just because we are all good.\\\"\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Even my sister's a decent chef\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"pure potluck\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of Paris 2024, Campbell is a Home Team Hero for Old El Paso as they unite with Team GB over a shared goal of creating more connection this summer.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999108695, \"rank\": 8.915148524138804e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Old El Paso\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\"}, {\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999991391863726, \"rank\": 6.328297697039657e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"a Home Team Hero\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"a shared goal\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"more connection\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB unites the nation in support of their athletes, while Old El Paso is best enjoyed with friends and families around the table.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258,