": 1614, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each of the Home Team Heroes - also including Olympic swimming champion Tom Dean, Olympic diving champion and three-time medallist Jack Laugher and Olympic BMX racing champion Bethany Shriever - feature on individual packs and all share a golden tip on how they bring their unique flavour to an Old El Paso meal.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroes_(American_TV_series)\", \"score\": 0.996108815638869, \"rank\": 0.0030001972448011178, \"text\": \"Heroes\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroes_(American_TV_series)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heroes_(American_TV_series)\"}, {\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Dean_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9999936593363623, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Dean_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Dean_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1757, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jack Laugher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\"}, {\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bethany Shriever\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\"}, {\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Old El Paso\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O